'''Double-Dip Outer Rim Rumdrop''' was a [[Alcohol/Legends|mixed drink]] invented by [[Shayne Gerrare]] for his place of employment, [[Spirited Spirits]], on the planet [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. The specialty drink was quite popular and was most responsible for Spirited Spirits' success.<ref name="trw">{{LivingForce|Eye of the Sun: The Resistance Within}}</ref> It was made with a wide range of alcohol stocks.<ref name="swg">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=item|Double-Dip Outer Rim Rumdrop}}</ref>

In [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]], the Rim Rumdrop had been exported to other planets of the system. It was available in the [[Cabana Bar]] of the [[Sanads of Rorkee]] hotel, on [[Genarius]], where it was the drink of choice of hotel guest Dr. [[Shilaea Motacc]]. When Motacc was kidnapped, a stranger went to the Cabana Bar to buy all the available stock of Double-Dip Outer Rim Rumdrops.<ref name="hitc">{{LivingForce|Clouds of Genarius: Head in the Clouds}}</ref>

